Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time for 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average time for 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases where the next activity is 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases without 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER does not occur

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' in cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Payment Handled' in cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time it takes 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' after 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE occurs

Name: Average time for 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases that were eventually approved after being initially rejected by any role
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by any_role occurs

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases with direct transition to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' in cases without 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases leading to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' to identify bottlenecks in the approval process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER occurs

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Payment Handled' in cases exceeding the average processing time

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases that required director's approval
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
